data.revised_prompt: Generate a professional, high-quality image of a 'Ginger Whiskey Toddy' cocktail. The cocktail is showcased in a clear, heat-resistant glass mug, perfectly illuminating its warm amber hue. A steaming swirl of liquid exudes a comforting array of autumnal tones. Atop, a thin wheel of lime partners with a slice of fresh ginger, releasing fragrant citrus and spicy aromas. The lighting is soft, casting a homely glow and initiating subtle reflections on the wooden surface below. In the backdrop, a blurred tapestry of deep greens evokes a rustic forest setting, amplifying the inviting warmth and earthy allure of the cocktail. The image should exude tranquility and a sophisticated rustic charm, appearing as if it was taken by a professional food photographer. The image needs to be realistic, without any text or watermarks, and with a clear background having a soft focus.
